<C-c C-c i>, wich is the default key binding for `bhl-insert-image'.

   Only `bhl2html' handles images.  Other conversion functions like
`bhl2sgml', `bhl2texinfo' or `bhl2latex' put images into comment
strings. `bhl2txt' erases images.


